desc_long							评测						“DvDrum allows you to play in real time a Virtual Drum to shows your Drummer Experience and Ability.”8/10 Very Good – Softonic“DvDrum allows let's play a virtual drum with pc keyboard in simplicity and realism.”5/5 – soft32“DvDrum is a drum simulator in which you you can choose your instruments, your virtual interface, your key set and play. You can load a musical base, releasable in site link, and recording a video of your performance.”5/5 – gamershell												关于这款游戏							DvDrum is Quality, Customizable Drum Simulator. It Allows to Play in Jam Session Mode a Virtual Drum with Keyboard, MIDI Controller, Joystick,  Guitar Hero® and Rock Band® Drumkits and USB Pedals, in Realistic Mode for a Real Drummer Experience!With External Scripts is Possible to Transform DvDrum into a Drum Machine!DvDrum isn't a VST or Plugin, This is a Standalone Complete Game for Drumming.Change the composition of your drumkit, remove/add components. Change component graphic and sound, change the carpet, the floor and add some decorations. Hundreds of images and sounds, for endless possibilities for customization!You can create endless combinations of sound to your drumkit. Choose a sound from the hundreds of sounds and change the pan and pitch, to create a completely new! Import a saved SoundSet file to change immediately the sound!Exports the drumkit graphic settings, or audio settings or only keys settings. You can export and import only the settings those interest you, and make many combinations of settings customized. Coming soon support for Steam WorkShopRecord your performance, show your drummer skills with DvDrum!Compared with other thousands of DvDrummer, learns and improve you from the users feedback. Share your video on Youtube or Play Live on Twitch! Main DvDrum Features: High Quality Sounds!Hundreds of High Quality Wav Sounds, Sampled from Real Drumkits. Highly Customizable!Create your Drumkit! Change the composition of your drumkit, remove/add components.Change component graphic and sound, change the carpet, the floor and add some decorations.Hundreds of images and sounds, for endless possibilities for customization! Mixer!You can create endless combinations of sound to your drumkit.Choose a sound from the hundreds of sounds and change the pan and pitch, to create a completely new! Support for External Devices!DvDrum supports various types of External Devices such as MIDI Controller, Joystick, RockBand® and GuitarHero® Drumkit!Can you imagine playing the bass kicks with racing pedals? Support for External Scripts!With "AutoHotkey" software is Possible to Transform DvDrum into a Drum Machine!  Export/Import!Exports the drumkit graphic settings, or audio settings or only keys settings. You can export and import only the settings those interest you, and make many combinations of settings customized.  Metronome!Train to keep time with the internal metronome! High Reactivity!Optimized to minimize latency between input-audio for best experience. Simple InterfaceThe user friendly and intuitive interface makes each operation easier.New features and improvements will be added with future updates						
